milestones.description: Engineer and Gavaskar's 123-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad
Gavaskar has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 149 runs, going past Brijesh Patel's 110
Syed Abid Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for IND, going past Engineer
Frasat Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for E&CA, going past Harilal Shah
Madan Lal has become the top wicket-taker for IND in ODIs with 6 wickets, going past Syed Abid Ali's 3
Jawahir Shah has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (20) in an innings in ODIs for E&CA, going past Zulfiqar Ali's 16
Engineer and Gavaskar's 123-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 70 between Ajit Wadekar and Engineer
Ramesh Sethi and Jawahir Shah's 42-run partnership is EAF's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between Zulfiqar Ali and Mehmood Quaraishy
Engineer and Gavaskar's 123-run partnership is IND's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 44 between Gavaskar and Sudhir Naik
Walusimbi and Praful Mehta's 10-run partnership is E&CA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Frasat Ali and Ramesh Sethi
Ramesh Sethi and Jawahir Shah's 42-run partnership is E&CA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 25 between Frasat Ali and Mehmood Quaraishy
